node.text:
Meet our hop torpedoes. Since 2009 we've been stuffing each torpedo with around 75 lbs of hops (depending on the brew) to infuse beers like its namesake Torpedo IPA with next level flavor and aroma. 
We're not mathematicians but we know that equals a whole lot of hoppy goodness. 🤤
#TorpedoTuesday

Dig out your dirndls and lederhosen because this year's Oktoberfest brew is headed your way. 
This rich Märzen lager features German malts for inviting aromas of honey and biscuity bread, flavors of caramel and graham cracker, and visions of sprawling beer tents.

From mountains to rivers and everywhere in between, we’re loving the ways you’re getting outside this summer. 

There’s still time to enter your epic outdoor photos for a chance to win Sierra Nevada swag and goodies from @yeti, @ospreypacks and @campspot.

Tag your pic with #GoSummerContest and @sierranevada or upload at the link in our profile. Contest closes July 31.
